{"tid":1264154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G20峰會：習近平主動握手 川普眉頭緊鎖","createTime":"2019-06-28T14:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T14:22:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"808730b1538a3b357ec781e7a80a98a54815c2f4","tid":1264154,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"G20峰會今天（6月28日）在日本大阪開幕，各國領導人峰會合影的細節被曝光。網上傳出的視頻顯示，習近平滿臉笑容，主動上前與川普（特朗普）握手打招呼，而川普眉頭緊鎖，表情顯得有些嚴肅。<br />\n<br />\n當地時間6月28日，在大阪G20峰會的合影時間，美國總統川普與中國國家主席習近平首次短暫握手寒暄。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音發出的現場視頻顯示，習近平主動走到川普這裡來打招呼，兩人握手。川普眉頭緊鎖，對習說了幾句話，隨後習回到了自己的位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2019/06/1-449-600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F1-449-600x338.jpg&h=27884260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/06/28/a102611112.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F06%2F28%2Fa102611112.html&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6vzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=d32b55be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/06/28/a102611112.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ac1197d24240111291511e1662041becda80f7e","tid":1264154,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"who...who a u"}]}